# Force-hoist specific transitive dependencies so Vite's optimizeDeps can
# pre-bundle them. Cesium is excluded from optimizeDeps (its module layout
# breaks under esbuild), but a couple of its CJS subdeps (notably
# `mersenne-twister`) need to be pre-bundled themselves so the browser
# receives valid ESM. pnpm's strict store doesn't hoist transitive deps by
# default, so Vite's resolver can't find them.
public-hoist-pattern[]=mersenne-twister
